				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ RR=\frac{c/E\left[c\right]}{\left(C-c\right)/\left(C-E\left[c\right]\right)} $$\end{document}RR=c/EcC−c/C−Ecwhere the meaning of the symbols are the same as above.
